  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. This synthetic adversarial sample embeds W-EP-02: one ValidationResult carries detailed narrative about the experimental campaign that produced it but omits the structured prov:wasGeneratedBy link to its generation Activity.",
